article_id:2641,category_name:News,title_name:Issue with the Drop Rewards in Lilith's Encroaching Shadow: Legend[Update],image_path:,message:<div>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1637913600"></span>]<br>This issue, which took place from approximately <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1637560800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1637906400"></span>, has now been resolved.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><hr><div>We have confirmed an issue in Lilith&#39;s Encroaching Shadow: Legend occurring since approximately <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1637560800"></span>, where defeating the boss Lilith drops twice the normal amount of rewards.</div><div><br></div><div>We plan to correct this issue in a data update around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1637906400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Any further updates concerning this issue will be added to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div>,start_time:1637745300,update_time1637913534